---
import SubpageLayout from '../../../layouts/SubpageLayout.astro';
---

<SubpageLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Proof of Concept"
  subtitle="Validate your AI idea before committing to a full build. Rapid proof-of-concept in a 6-day sprint."
  seoDescription="AI Prototyping: validate your AI idea with a rapid proof-of-concept. 6-day sprint methodology that de-risks your investment. By AI Heroes."
  accentColor="blue"
  pillarBadge="Software & Implementation"
  ctaLabel="Discuss your project"
  trustedBy={["Trabu", "TicketGenie", "050-IT"]}
>
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-6">Prove it works before you build it</h2>

    <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      Many AI projects start too big. Months of development, large teams, significant budgets, only to discover the approach doesn't work. We flip this: start small, prove the value, then scale. In 6 days you'll have a working prototype.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-stone-50 p-6 md:p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-brand-blue not-prose">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-3">The 6-day sprint</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-600 list-disc ml-5">
        <li><strong>Day 1-2:</strong> Define scope, explore data, choose architecture</li>
        <li><strong>Day 3-4:</strong> Build the core prototype</li>
        <li><strong>Day 5:</strong> Integration and testing with real data</li>
        <li><strong>Day 6:</strong> Demo, evaluation and go/no-go for full build</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-4">Why prototype?</h3>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8 not-prose">
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">De-risk your investment</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Discover early whether your approach works, before committing €50K+ to a full build.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Tangible proof</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">A working prototype convinces stakeholders better than any PowerPoint deck.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Fast feedback</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Users can test the prototype and provide feedback. Builds buy-in.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Reusable code</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">The prototype isn't throwaway; it forms the foundation for the full solution.</p></div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-4">What we prototype</h3>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8 not-prose">
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">AI assistants</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Chatbots and copilots with your business context.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Document processing</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Automatic extraction, classification and summarisation.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Workflow automation</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">AI-driven process steps that replace manual work.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Data analysis pipelines</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Automated insights from your existing data.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8 not-prose">
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-blue mb-2">6 days</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">To prototype</div></div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-blue mb-2">From €8,000</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Investment</div></div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-blue mb-2">Working</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Proof of concept</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="dark-box-content bg-brand-dark p-8 border-l-4 border-brand-red my-8 not-prose">
      <h3>From prototype to production</h3>
      <p>Happy with the prototype? Scale up to a full solution with <a href="/en/services/custom-ai-solutions" class="text-white underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-white/80">Custom AI Solutions</a>. Don't have a strategy yet? <a href="/en/services/ai-roadmap" class="text-white underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-white/80">Start with an AI Roadmap</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</SubpageLayout>
